    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I really thought bootstrap were going to a non structure-dependent API?\n\n> It is unclear for me how/or what exactly is different when using jQuery, is it possible to avoid React as \"renderer\" at all or only for custom widgets?\n\nYes, if you want to build custom widgets that are not using React where you control the full html rendering thats completely feasible.\n\nWith custom widgets you are free do to anything outside of React.\n",
