    "body": "Bootstrap heavily relays on a (good) structure, have a look at form styling for example: https://getbootstrap.com/css/#forms\n\nWhen there is no solution to avoid React divs around refinementList template items, this ticket can be set to \"wontfix\". :-/\n",
