  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> (I figured out it also depended on our rather old version of Bootstrap 2.3...)\n\nYes I think bootstrap should be less and less concerned about very precise HTML trees but still sometime may require it, also see all the possible \"cssClasses.*\" options on every widget because you might find gems that will help you put the right bootstrap class at the right level.\n",
