  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "In V2, we will provide either or both:\n- a `renderer` option where you can control the full markup rendering\n- a bootstrap renderer that will default to bootstrap type syntax for every element\n\nWe have a private proposal for renderers that we will make public soon.\n",
